N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 430.1 - Applicability

State Regulations

Licensed home care services agencies, certified home
health agencies and long-term home health care programs shall comply with the
standards for such agencies set forth in the State Hospital Code, Subchapter C
of this Chapter. Notes
